# OCI Artifact Format

- CL packages are OCI Image Indexes with universal + platform overlay manifests.
- `artifactType`: `application/vnd.common-lisp.system.v1`
- Config mediaType: `application/vnd.common-lisp.system.config.v1+json`
- Layers: standard `application/vnd.oci.image.layer.v1.tar+gzip`
- CL-specific metadata uses `dev.common-lisp.*` annotation namespace.
- Universal manifest: no `platform` field, always first in index.
- Platform overlays: use OCI `platform` field + `dev.common-lisp.implementation` annotation.
- Layer roles tracked in config blob `layer-roles` map (digest -> role string).
- See `docs/spec.md` for the full specification.
